{"title":"Security Screening Logs - User details comments","type":"markdown","aggs":[],"params":{"fontSize":8,"openLinksInNewTab":false,"markdown":"- 4720: New users: The TargetUserName is the **new account** , user.name=User that **created** the new account
- 4728: Group membership change. Users added to security enabled group
- 4732: Local Group membership change: The TargetUserName is the **new group membership** , the change is by the **User** in user.name
- 4624: A user logged on 
- 4624 **and** RDP (Logon Type 10): Enable both "Logons (4624)" and "RDP" to get RDP logons.
- 4625: Failed logins
- 4740: An account is locked after excessive **failed logins**
